{"tid":566679,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"29歲宅男燒炭亡　母4日後始揭發","createTime":"2018-02-20T07:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T07:40:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"22efcdee5d7a64dc891624f2e781a4447d71cc2d","tid":566679,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:11:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180220/20309857\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180220%2F20309857&d=BIV5xndJp99C8eXOj408iB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=d3ad3853\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180220%2F20309857&h=0e81d7f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180220/20309857</a><br />\n<br />\n29歲宅男燒炭亡　母4日後始揭發<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】牛頭角一名無業隱蔽青年，終日反鎖在房間內打機，母親一周前獨自返鄉下過年，3天前回家見兒子房間反鎖，還以為他如常在房內打機，未有理會；直至昨日她叩門查看未見有反應，擔心出事報警，才揭發兒子至少4天前已在房內燒炭自殺身亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180220/large/20la4p06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180220%2Flarge%2F20la4p06.jpg&h=a1da654c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仵工將男死者遺體移送殮房。<br />\n劉永明攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n返鄉後回港　以為子關門打機<br />\n<br />\n29歲死者姓李，數年前與現年54歲姓廖母親及胞妺入住彩德邨彩信樓一單位，其後胞妹結婚遷出，剩下母子二人。據悉，李無業，要靠母親工作供養。消息稱，李多年來甚少外出，終日在房內打機度日，而母親因工作關係，甚少與兒子溝通，對兒子足不出戶沉迷打機，也未有太在意。<br />\n<br />\n大約一周前李母返鄉過年，當日她離家時兒子仍在房內，她不以為意獨自離家回鄉。<br />\n李母至大前日（年初二）晚由內地返港，回家發現兒子房門關上，以為兒子仍在打機；直至昨晨8時許，她見兒子仍未出房，拍門又無反應，擔心兒子發生意外於是報警。警員及消防員到場破門，發現事主倒斃床上，床邊有一鐵罐盛載燒過的炭，調查後認為案件無可疑，根據其屍體狀況，初步估計他在上周四（年三十）當日燒炭自殺，至昨晨揭發時已有4天之久。<br />\n<br />\n對於今次事件，香港家庭及事業發展服務訓練總監司徒漢明稱，隱蔽青年與父母關係差，相處不愉快，返家後都會關上房門沉醉在自己的小天地；若父母懶理，關係會更差。<br />\n<br />\n司徒漢明指出，不少隱蔽青年都是因為遇到挫折，又不願去面對，最後索性選擇逃避，不會主動求助，因此父母應主動去改善與子女的關係，找出子女隱蔽的原因，以重建關係；若解決不了，便要尋求專業人士幫助。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黃麗英、徐雲庭"},{"pid":"424e6636ec4f96f834ac668af60f32b46cc76bf2","tid":566679,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:12:24.000Z","msg":"邊位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b018cae5ae8e8fa41a5e6df4dadf347350a901e8","tid":566679,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"424e6636ec4f96f834ac668af60f32b46cc76bf2","tid":566679,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:12:24.000Z","msg":"邊位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:22:43.000Z","msg":"佢唔會答到你喎"},{"pid":"ab788a3d0ad57d5542f3df9a903fd9086f1a2511","tid":566679,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b018cae5ae8e8fa41a5e6df4dadf347350a901e8","tid":566679,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"424e6636ec4f96f834ac668af60f32b46cc76bf2","tid":566679,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:12:24.000Z","msg":"邊位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:22:43.000Z","msg":"佢唔會答到你喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/153044_42c2a26cfa2a7cf314c6257d85317c3e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F153044_42c2a26cfa2a7cf314c6257d85317c3e.gif&h=e6b0dc76&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"414b79a0a40f39e43c5026ca76a5cf5a9cb35efd","tid":566679,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"424e6636ec4f96f834ac668af60f32b46cc76bf2","tid":566679,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:12:24.000Z","msg":"邊位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:32:41.000Z","msg":"he is not the first and will not be the last"},{"pid":"aa3b5c8b2f3e2304f31dbd2fb6d103ac6812e330","tid":566679,"uid":146604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:34:40.000Z","msg":"其實我只想燒炭取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打機打到手指凍到硬晒 影響我神一般的操作"},{"pid":"6373ddf3a761a6586dc0271ea36a081fcb128e08","tid":566679,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:35:44.000Z","msg":"而家一個人住三人單位，老母要調遷喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw個不在場證明幾完美"},{"pid":"4e6172905e3cddbe59286a69294352bef7a262bf","tid":566679,"uid":7278,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:40:40.000Z","msg":"找出子女隱蔽的原因<br />\n<br />\n父母應該最清楚<br />\n生完唔理 乜都推晒俾學校<br />\n自己淨係搵錢為兩餐<br />\n<br />\n倒頭來又係窮人唔好生仔<br />\n其實只不過係香港真係太過難生存<br />\n乜都要搶 爭 <br />\n<br />\n都係社會自然生態嘅結果<br />\n冇人有錯"}]}